		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64517139"><p>We could be recycling more. There is a lot of copper wiring that is becoming redundant as we switch to fibre optic. It's relatively easy to recycle too, it just needs the sheath stripping off and then you have large amounts of known quantity copper wiring that can either be re-used or recycled into new wires.</p></div>
	</div>

